sentence: Hamas-run  health  ministry  in  Gaza  says  14  killed  since  truce  ended.

article_title: Hamas-run health ministry in Gaza says 14 killed since truce ended.
sentence: A  spokesman  for  the  Hamas-run  health  ministry  in  Gaza  says  14  people  have  been  killed  in  the  territory  in  the  first  two  hours  since  the  temporary  ceasefire  ended.
